.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畫面少少驚嚇 睇完再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e7a46bc8fc77cb2bca08d59b5e1a59a5e29b70","tid":456170,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:54:40.000Z","msg":"好 撚 衝 擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c907ef71a7e9e0bf8c87294ac6082f46baffe76b","tid":456170,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59edc30149af087e839801a6d2cc82cab0e6059","tid":456170,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/004917_13cf74dc8ffcbd74ad060abf2756fb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F004917_13cf74dc8ffcbd74ad060abf2756fb2e.jpg&h=d316c013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開咗第三季第一集啦<br />\n今季得四集 愈出愈少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚睇到我好淆 好撚cult<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畫面少少驚嚇 睇完再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"自<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都係有六集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完第三季其實都覺得同第二季嘅設定幾似<br />\n條樓梯同never ending house都係會突然出現係唔同地方<br />\n女主角又係陷入咗去裡世界<br />\n個結局又係冇完結到 間屋都係周圍出現 啲塗鴉冇消失 最後隻嘢冇死同冇返到入屋 所以都係冇結局 成年隻嘢食咗幾多人 佢到底係咩嘅representation cannibalism sprit?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAlice好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本最大壓力最想正常咁生活嘅係佢多過zoe 因為peaches屋企人呢個錯覺令佢深陷錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後咁warm好諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n血腥同唯美嘅畫面令到呢季好突出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然我睇完十萬個問號</span><br />\n欣賞channel zero奇怪嘅題材"},{"pid":"8ae645a882f67e8461ba7560a966cdea1c969be3","tid":456170,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cbe531e5b4f5572f3df0369b28458f9982efc0","tid":456170,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T16:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推到第四季"},{"pid":"3a4bc16a603f60e4999feeb18614e68aedb39918","tid":456170,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e3a3c46c84cde61733f25e92c88caed34d4866","tid":456170,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fnyNA5YM9UQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfnyNA5YM9UQ&d=NcqQRCZ2A5PjWhcJ3PxkfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=dc6fae29\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fnyNA5YM9UQ</a><br />\n第四季第一集出咗啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 26號等齊先睇"},{"pid":"25d93f34c3f9f2e0d2babf985b10be1730618db0","tid":456170,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T18:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RitGQ8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRitGQ8d.png&h=2881f45a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">諗乜有乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係鬥邊個係ff大師 <br />\n每個小朋友都曾經有過imaginary friend<br />\n每人一隻guardian其實幾warm 但變到好血腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但因為好似屋企人咁保護佢<br />\n去到最後居然覺得隻小丑好慘 <br />\n明明勁撚creepy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別係攬實個下<br />\ndllm到底邊個諗埋啲咁fucked up嘅形象出黎(讚緊) <br />\n連jumpscare都唔使就搞到個人勁心寒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span><br />\n<br />\n唔需要合理解釋嘅現象係最精彩嘅畫面<br />\nchannel zero嘅世界觀就係冇得解釋<br />\n最後提醒大家FF太多真係會傷身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}